import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Navbar from './Navbar'
import Hero from './Hero'
import Newsletter from './Newsletter'
import Footer from './Footer'


const Container = styled.div`

`

const Wrapper = styled.div`
    padding: 3rem;
    display: flex;
`

const ImgContainer = styled.div`
    flex: 1;
`

const Image = styled.img`
    width: 70%;
    object-fit: cover;

`

const InfoContainer = styled.div`
    flex: 1;
`

const Title = styled.h1``

const Desc = styled.p``

const Price = styled.span``



const IndividualProduct = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
    <Navbar/>
    <Hero/>
        <Wrapper>
            <ImgContainer>
                <Image src='/images/Baron.png'/>
            </ImgContainer>
            <InfoContainer>
                <Title>Baronne De Fleur</Title>
                <Desc>One of the best synchro monsters in the Yugioh TCG. It's good both going first and second because of its ability to destroy cards as well as provide omni-negation.</Desc>
                <Price>$5</Price>
            </InfoContainer>
        </Wrapper>
    <Newsletter/>
    <Footer/>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default IndividualProduct
